{@--1@} To do,
perform or carry out, execute, 
attend to (order, duty &c.); bring
about, effect, accomplish (business);
{#vivAhadIkzAviDimanvatizWat#} <ls>Ku. 7. 1</ls>, <ls n="Ku.">1. 17</ls>;
{#kimanutizWati BagavAn mArIcaH#} <ls>Ś. 7</ls>;  
