<ls>Ś. 1</ls>; {#ye me matamidaM nityamanutizWaMti mAnavAH#}  
<ls>Bg. 3. 31</ls> follow; {#guMrorvacanamanutizWa#} <ls>V. 5</ls> do
as your papa orders; {#anutizWasvAtmano#}
{#niyogaM#} <ls>M. 1</ls> look or attend to your
own duty, do your business.
{@--2@} To follow, practise, observe
({#Darma, vrata#} &c.); commit (a sin). 
{@--3@} To
rule, govern, superintend; appoint.
{@--4@} To stand by or near (with <ab>loc.</ab>);
<ls>Ms. 11. 112</ls>; sit on; occupy;  
{#anuzWAsyati rAmasya sItA prakftamAsanaM#} <ls>Rām.</ls>
