{#svakAMtAmanutizWati#} <ls>Rām.</ls>; {#nArAjake patiM BAryA#} 
{#yaTAvadanutizWati#} <ls>Subhāṣ.</ls>; follow, obey.
{@--6@} To imitate, tread in; {#padaM#} 
{#cehAnutizWaMti pUrvezAM pUrvajEH kftaM#} <ls>Bhāg.</ls> 
{@--7@} 
(Intrans.) ({%a%}) To place or put oneself
on, be in a position, present 
oneself. ({%b%}) To remain, continue. ({%c%})
To be engaged in religious 
ceremonies (muttering prayers &c.);  
